<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00016</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING SECTION ONE OF REPUBLIC ACT NUMBERED NINE THOUSAND THREE HUNDRED FORTY-SIX OTHERWISE KNOWN AS "AN ACT PROHIBITING THE IMPOSITION OF DEATH PENALTY IN THE PHILIPPINES"</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Restores the death penalty for heinous crimes covered under Republic Act No. 9165, otherwise known as the Comprehensive Dangerous Drugs Act of 2002, as amended, by amending Section 1 of RA09346, An Act Prohibiting the Imposition of Death Penalty in the Philippines.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BIAZON, ROZZANO RUFINO B.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Reform</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>MOTHER BILL:&nbspHB04727</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON JUSTICE ON 2016-07-26</td></tr></table>